Now u have learn how to accept a PR, I ll show you how to set the upstream so that ur a branch conventionally called upstream (u can name it as u wish), remains in sync with the Original author. Then u c can do a git diff upstream with ur current branch.
As discussed over phone, just write git remote add upstream ORIGINAL_AUTHORS_URL
